  "name": "Chronic Kidney Disease",
  "description": "This test case evaluates the identification of chronic kidney disease patients using a complex algorithm that considers eGFR values, albuminuria staging, and excludes patients with acute conditions. It tests the ability to query for multiple laboratory measurements (creatinine for eGFR calculation, urine albumin-to-creatinine ratio, urine protein-to-creatinine ratio) and apply clinical staging criteria according to NKF KDOQI and KDIGO guidelines.",
